flowchart TD
    A[Create Employee Request] --> B[Validate JWT Token]
    B --> C{Token Valid?}
    C -->|No| D[Return 401 Unauthorized]
    C -->|Yes| E[Check Company Admin Permissions]
    E --> F{Admin Access for Company?}
    F -->|No| G[Return 403 Forbidden]
    F -->|Yes| H[Validate Employee Data]
    H --> I{Valid Employee Data?}
    I -->|No| J[Return 400 Invalid Data]
    I -->|Yes| K[Check Email Uniqueness]
    K --> L{Email Available?}
    L -->|No| M[Return 409 Email Already Exists]
    L -->|Yes| N[Hash Password]
    N --> O[Generate Employee ID]
    O --> P[Insert Employee Record]
    P --> Q[Set Default Permissions]
    Q --> R[Send Welcome Email]
    R --> S[Cache Employee Data]
    S --> T[Log Employee Creation]
    T --> U[Return 201 Employee Created]
    
    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style D fill:#ffebee
    style G fill:#ffebee
    style J fill:#ffebee
    style M fill:#ffebee
    style U fill:#e8f5e8